課程概述 Course Description
       介紹物理系統中之相變現象與理論基礎
瞭解物理系統中之相變現象，並能用理論從事計算分析.
1. Phase transition in fluid, magnetic matter, crystal, …thermal physics.2. Exact solution, duality, Mean field methods. 3. Phase transition in Ising model, XY-model, Heisenberg model, XY-model, Potts model, Gauge theory, Hall effect, superconductor......4. Renormalization group method and computer Simulation method. 5. Phase transition in lattice gauge thoery.  
Standley, Critical phenomena and phase transition. Kogut, Review of modern physics
 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
understand phase transitioncalculate phase transition temperature. RG. dualitycalculate phase transition quantity. manybody system 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Statistics and phase transition2Phase transition system3Correction function and phase transition4Ising model, Mean field solution.  Exaction solution and phase transition temperature5Ising model, serise expansion. Duality.6Ising gauge model.  Duality and  phase transition7Renormalization Group.8Renormalization Group. 9xy model. Topology  phase transition 10Spin glass. Liquid crystal phase transition.11Quantum spin phase transition12quantum Hall effect phase transition13Fraction quantum Hall effect phase transition14Superconductor phase transition15Superfluid phase transition16Conformal field theory and  phase transition 17Conformal field theory and classify phase transition18Manybody system phase transition relation 

