相變理論                                


  	介紹物理系統中之相變現象與理論基礎
瞭解物理系統中之相變現象，並能用理論從事計算分析.
1. Phase transition in fluid, magnetic matter, crystal, …thermal physics.2. Exact solution, duality, Mean field methods. 3. Phase transition in Ising model, XY-model, Heisenberg model, XY-model, Potts model, Gauge theory, Hall effect, superconductor......4. Renormalization group method and computer Simulation method. 5. Phase transition in lattice gauge thoery.  
Standley, Critical phenomena and phase transition. Kogut, Review of modern physics


課程教育目標 

A. 培育具備健全品格、堅實學問、關懷社會與全球視野的人材。B. 訓練未來社會中堅及領導人才，以推動人類的永續發展。C. 培育具有科學精神與廣泛物理學知識，成為科學界中堅的人材。 
